Before we visited
schools, we wanted the day

00:14:43.950 --> 00:14:46.250
to feel really special.

00:14:46.250 --> 00:14:49.460
And we wanted the
kids to be excited

00:14:49.460 --> 00:14:51.690
about their virtual
field trip just like they

00:14:51.690 --> 00:14:53.680
would a normal field trip.

00:14:53.680 --> 00:14:56.150
And so we provided the
students with the gear

00:14:56.150 --> 00:14:59.270
that they would need to be
able to go on this expedition.

00:14:59.270 --> 00:15:01.400
Just like a normal
physical field trip,

00:15:01.400 --> 00:15:04.070
you've got to take notes, and
write down your observations,

00:15:04.070 --> 00:15:07.140
and be able to share
them with your peers.

00:15:07.140 --> 00:15:10.130
And so the same thing
applied with Expeditions.

00:15:10.130 --> 00:15:11.840
And that feedback
