00:35:51.960 --> 00:35:53.800
in the early stages of VR.

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:56.210
Hardware will improve,
computational power

00:35:56.210 --> 00:35:58.556
will improve, design
patterns will improve,

00:35:58.556 --> 00:36:00.180
and some of the
developers in this room

00:36:00.180 --> 00:36:02.650
are going to find ways
to use VR in education

00:36:02.650 --> 00:36:04.940
that we haven't
even imagined yet.

00:36:04.940 --> 00:36:06.830
The slide here is a
